  "detailed_description": "<h1>Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>Reviews</h1><p>\"Best game ever made.\" - 11/10 Development Team</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428770/extras/1cc2213ea545cbed695b6bed18d41c95.poster.avif?t=1659045236\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428770/extras/1cc2213ea545cbed695b6bed18d41c95.webm?t=1659045236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1428770/extras/1cc2213ea545cbed695b6bed18d41c95.mp4?t=1659045236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game is hard! Play solo or with friends to unlock up to 6 unique characters and 150+ guns, items, and pets!<br><br>You are tasked with exploring an unknown continent by The Kingdom. Based on the character you select the reason for being on the continent changes! Conquest, power, knowledge, vengeance, and more!",
